getRenderedSite.py is a great hack from http://blog.motane.lu/2009/06/18/pywebkitgtk-execute-javascript-from-python/

Instructions for how to install webkit for getting rendered sites
    http://code.google.com/p/pywebkitgtk/ and download, untar
    cd to directory
    install python-dev, libxslt-dev, python-gtk2-dev, libwebkit-dev
    run ./configure --prefix=/pywebkitgtk/install/path
    make
    make install (root)
    http://blog.motane.lu/2009/06/18/pywebkitgtk-execute-javascript-from-python/

